Altimeter GPS privacy policy
hikerdesk
Oct 8, 2018
1 min read
Data storage
Altimeter GPS - Hike & Trek stores the user data locally on iPhone. We do not store any kind of user data on servers. Thus the data is completely safe from any kind of misuse or abuse.
Information Collection and Use
App asks for user permission to access the following necessary features :
Location
Photos
Motion & Fitness
Camera
Notifications
Links to Other Sites
Our Service doesnâ€™t contain links to other sites.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, we advise you to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. These changes are effective immediately, after they are posted on this page.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at hikerdesk[at]gmail[dot]com
